⁣⁣THE SPACE COLLECTION° [ 1.18.21 ] - Launch I : Gold Carbon Extract ~ 𝟭𝟲 𝗣𝘀𝘆𝗰𝗵𝗲 ☄️⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀
The asteroid P16 is orbiting between Mars and Jupiter is made of pure metals worth an estimated $10,000 quadrillion (that's 15 more zeroes), more than the entire economy of Earth. 🤑🛸 ⠀⠀
⠀
With some help 👽 these materials have been extracted directly from 𝟭𝟲 𝗣𝘀𝘆𝗰𝗵𝗲 and are now available to be wrapped directly onto your phone 📲 ⠀⠀
⠀⠀
#TheSpaceCollection #WrapYourPhone #AtascaCustoms #OutOfThisWorldWraps
